ActNational Energy Board Act
SubjectAmending Order AO-001-GC- 8 - Pine Cliff Energy Ltd.
PrecisOrder approving the ISSUANCE by the National Energy Board of Amending Order AO-001-GC- 8 to reflect the transfer of ownership of a natural gas pipeline (referred to as NPS 16) of approximately 1.32 km in length which crosses the Alberta-Saskatchewan border. It will vary the certificate holder name from Mid-Continent, to the acquiring company, Pine Cliff Energy Ltd.
